### =========================================================================
### LOCALHOST (Local Requests)
### =========================================================================

### Welcome to the API
GET http://localhost:3000/

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### MOVIES
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Get all movies
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### 2. Get a single movie by ID (Replace with an existing ID from your DB)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3073

### 3. Create a new movie
POST http://localhost:3000/movies HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "genre": "Sci-Fi",
  "rating": "PG-13",
  "duration": 148,
  "language": "English",
  "plot": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O."
}

### 4. Update a movie (Replace the ID at the end with an existing one)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3073 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception (Special Edition)",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "genre": "Sci-Fi / Thriller",
  "rating": "PG-13",
  "duration": 150,
  "language": "English",
  "plot": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O."
}

### 5. Delete a movie (Replace the ID at the end with an existing one)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3073 HTTP/1.1


### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### DIRECTORS
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Get all directors
GET http://localhost:3000/directors

### 2. Get a single director by ID (Replace with an existing ID from your DB)
GET http://localhost:3000/directors/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3074

### 3. Create a new director
POST http://localhost:3000/directors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "name": "Christopher Nolan",
  "birthYear": 1970,
  "nationality": "British-American",
  "notableWorks": ["Inception", "Interstellar", "The Dark Knight"],
  "active": true
}

### 4. Update a director (Replace the ID at the end with an existing one)
PUT http://localhost:3000/directors/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3074 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "name": "Christopher Nolan",
  "birthYear": 1970,
  "nationality": "British-American",
  "notableWorks": ["Inception", "Interstellar", "The Dark Knight", "Oppenheimer"],
  "active": true
}

### 5. Delete a director (Replace the ID at the end with an existing one)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/directors/64a98fa697484bb30cdf3074 HTTP/1.1
